              > suffered for that.
              Learning Lisp would not have helped you. Modern AI uses
              mostly Python based libraries such as Tensorflow and
              PyTorch. C++ is used for performance critical stuff.
              Nobody uses Lisp for AI anymore. It was a dead end.



        ** Fifth Generation (Score:2)
