  ** AI's Strength (Score:2)
     (by thePsychologist ( 1062886 ))

     
     AI (i.e. machine learning/neural networks) is really good at
     optimizing stuff, so its natural strength shows when you have
     hundreds of thousands of entities in a system. Examples are the
     electricity grid, playing Go, and a department store's
     inventory.
     In our individual lives, AI seems more like another drop in the
     bucket of too much technology, and I think one day we'll realize
     that less is more when it comes to the stuff in our homes.

